reviewText: Can not watch it , not in English . Want to return it .

This is a great series I have loved Columbo from when I was a young girl watching it with my parents. That was one show we could watch together and enjoy. I have watched it over and over again.
What I like is that sometimes Columbo is funny, embarrassed or coy with some of his suspects. It's just terrific.

It would appear that these columbo's are on the Columbo mystery movie collections. It seems when the put out the rest season of Columbo they just called them mystery movies instead of season 8 etc. I only rated low so you would read my review.
